<%
title "Features"
description "Sheethub Features"
keywords %w(features benefits)
%>

<div class="white-container">
<div id="features" class="container">
    <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
        <h1>Made for Musicians</h1>
        <h2>Get started in seconds and let us take care of everything from the secure payment all the way to the download.</h2>

        <img src="http://s13.postimg.org/j6kfkowrr/sheetshow.png" />

        <div class="col-xs-6">
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-thumbs-o-up"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Easy Publishing</h3>
                    <p>Easily publish, manage, and update your music to a growing audience of musicians. Add files, video links, set a price, and more. No complex installation or technical skills required.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-smile-o"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Zero Upfront Fees</h3>
                    <p>SheetHub costs nothing up-front to use. You are free to upload an unlimited number of commercial works.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-money"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Pay Only When You Sell</h3>
                    <p>You keep 80% of your sales revenue - that leaves 20% for us. No setup fees, no monthly fees, no hosting fees to worry about!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-bank"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Get Paid Instantly</h3>
                    <p>Who likes waiting for their own money? No one. Get paid instantly and directly to your PayPal account the moment a user completes a purchase. </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-credit-card"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Say Yes To Every Customer</h3>
                    <p>Accept major credit cards from customers all over the world, including Visa, MasterCard, American Express, and Discover.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-area-chart"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Detailed Sales Analytics</h3>
                    <p>Gain valuable insight into your overall earnings, your most popular works, who your fans are, and more from your sales dashboard.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-6">
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-truck"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Secure Delivery of Files</h3>
                    <p>Files are saved over a secure link and only released to your customer via a timed or download limited link. This stops people passing on the download link to other people who aren’t planning on paying.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-certificate"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>PDF Stamping <span class="badge pro">NEW</span></h3>
                    <p>Discourage the illegal sharing of your PDF products by stamping them with the name and email of your customer. With their ‘fingerprint’ on it, people are less likely to sell or share your content.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-shopping-cart"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Pay-What-You-Want Pricing <span class="badge pro">NEW</span></h3>
                    <p>You always get to set the minimum price for your music, but that doesn’t stop your fans from giving more in the spirit of supporting you! Let your biggest fans decide how much they pay you.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-link"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Your Own Personal Website <span class="badge pro">NEW</span></h3>
                    <p>Signing up gives you your own personal website at username.sheethub.co that showcases all the works you've published on SheetHub.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-tree"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Getting Better Every Day</h3>
                    <p>SheetHub is a continuously evolving platform built to cater the needs of our growing community of musicians. The community decides and votes on what we build next. You shape the future of SheetHub!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>

    <% if !user_signed_in? %>
        <a href="<%= new_user_registration_url %>" class="btn btn-success center-block"> Sign Up For Free</a>
    <% end %>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
        <h1>Made for Discovery</h1>
        <h2>Discover new and interesting works by instruments, genres, composers, and sources, or view recommendations and related pieces.</h2>

        <img src="http://s27.postimg.org/e3uvisp5v/recommendations.png" />

        <div class="col-xs-6">
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-tags"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Tags</h3>
                    <p>Filter by genres, composers, instruments, and sources to easily find works you care about.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-6">
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-heart-o"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Recommendations <span class="badge pro">NEW</span></h3>
                    <p>Easily discover new and interesting music through recommended tags and pieces.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>

    <% if !user_signed_in? %>
        <a href="<%= new_user_registration_url %>" class="btn btn-success center-block"> Sign Up For Free</a>
    <% end %>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
        <h1>Made for You</h1>
        <h2>Owning your purchases should be easy, not difficult.</h2>

        <img src="http://s11.postimg.org/dmdvmbcpv/buynow.png" />

        <div class="col-xs-6">
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-birthday-cake"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>DRM-Free</h3>
                    <p>No Flash, no proprietary software to install, no restrictive copy protection. Buy once, keep forever.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-hand-o-up"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Instant Buy</h3>
                    <p>Sometimes you don’t need a shopping cart. Instant buy makes purchasing as simple and easy as possible. Just click, pay and download your product.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-6">
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-credit-card"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Multiple Payment Options</h3>
                    <p>Pay with PayPal, or with major credit cards including Visa, MasterCard, American Express, and Discover.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
    <% if !user_signed_in? %>
        <a href="<%= new_user_registration_url %>" class="btn btn-success center-block"> Sign Up For Free</a>
    <% end %>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
        <h1>Made for Friends</h1>
        <h2>Our platform is centered around sharing. Add works to your favorites, share it with your friends on your social networks, or give the author feedback in the comments.</h2>

        <img src="http://s12.postimg.org/8aje8qtul/share.png" />

        <div class="col-xs-6">
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-comments-o"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Discussions</h3>
                    <p>Give constructive feedback to the author, post your performance recordings, and discuss the piece with others.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-share"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Share buttons</h3>
                    <p>Share new and interesting pieces with your fellow musicians on major social networks.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-6">
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-bookmark-o"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Favorites <span class="badge pro">NEW</span></h3>
                    <p>Bookmark your most favorite works for later perusal and purchase.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>

</div>
</div>

<% if !user_signed_in? %>
<div class="animated-banner footer-banner">
    <h1>Join a growing community of musicians. <a href="<%= new_user_registration_url %>" class="btn btn-inline btn-success btn-banner btn-lg center-block"> Sign Up Today</a></h1>
</div>
<% end %>